ai-patthana17.12:0.2_0: Having given the immaterial states produced by the phenomena that are counterpart of
ai-patthana17.12:0.3_0: I am worth a sixteenth part
ai-patthana17.12:1.1_0: A skillful quality doesn’t give rise to a limited object, nor doing so by cause or reason.
ai-patthana17.12:2.1_0: A skillful quality doesn’t give rise to a fine reinforced sense. It doesn’t give rise to the cause or condition.
ai-patthana17.12:3.1_0: A skillful quality doesn’t give rise to immorality, nor give rise to unprofitable state.
